    <item>
      <title>EPA 试图收回 200 亿美元气候法裁决奖金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/epa-seeking-to-claw-back-20-billion-in-awards-from-climate-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国环保署署长李·泽尔丁周三晚间表示，美国环保署将试图收回根据总统乔·拜登签署的气候法授予的约 200 亿美元气候项目资金，并将这一努力描述为一项没有适当监督的“计划”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/epa-seeking-to-claw-back-20-billion-in-awards-from-climate-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 04:38:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的“买断”计划未能实现，75,000 名联邦工作人员接受了这项协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/musk-s-buyout-falls-short-as-75-000-federal-workers-took-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[约有 75,000 名联邦雇员签署了一项自愿辞职计划，该计划受到唐纳德·特朗普总统的亿万富翁效率沙皇的启发——该计划未能达到白宫希望的数字，并增加了更大规模解雇的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/musk-s-buyout-falls-short-as-75-000-federal-workers-took-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 03:29:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
