    <item>
      <title>美国起诉纽约非法移民身份证法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-sues-new-york-over-state-id-law-for-undocumented-immigrants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的政府正在就 2019 年的一项法律对纽约州提起诉讼，该法律允许无证移民获得州身份证明，同时向联邦当局保密他们的数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-sues-new-york-over-state-id-law-for-undocumented-immigrants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 02:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普“令人震惊”的关税扰乱贸易，印尼寻求新协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-seeks-new-deals-as-shocking-trump-tariffs-roil-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼贸易部副部长迪亚·罗罗·埃斯蒂·维迪亚·普特里表示，随着全球保护主义愈演愈烈，印尼正寻求实现市场多元化，同时也采取措施保护本土制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-seeks-new-deals-as-shocking-trump-tariffs-roil-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 02:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加巴德称对美国情报部门的信任度处于“历史最低点”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/tulsi-gabbard-says-trust-in-us-intelligence-community-is-at-all-time-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在参议院批准塔尔西·加巴德出任新任国家情报总监数小时后，她表示，对美国情报界的信任度“处于历史最低点”，并承诺结束她所谓的“武器化和政治化”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/tulsi-gabbard-says-trust-in-us-intelligence-community-is-at-all-time-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 23:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪在白宫峰会上寻求避开特朗普的贸易愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/modi-seeks-to-dodge-trump-s-trade-wrath-in-white-house-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五年前，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪最后一次与唐纳德·特朗普总统会面时，这位美国领导人站在莫迪的家乡古吉拉特邦10万欢呼的印度民众面前宣称：“美国永远是印度人民忠实的朋友。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/modi-seeks-to-dodge-trump-s-trade-wrath-in-white-house-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 13:00:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
